            Walter Habenicht
          + Walter Spiess
            Walter Spiess
       This paper presents a tabu search algorithm to optimize the
       structure of cold chains for distribution of chilled or frozen
       foods. The physical distribution system is structured in such a way
       that the cost for storage and transportation in the whole
