   This book describes as fully as possible each of the 564 no-take marine
   reserves in the Visayas. It also evaluates the functionality of these
   marine reserves based primarily on fish biomass and coral/seagrass/
   mangrove cover within their boundaries. It is designed as a quick
   reference book to a wide range of readers.

